OL,3,CCautious optimism for Nissan in
OL,4,CSunderland despite 20,000 global job
OL,5,Closses
OL,7,FOn Tuesday, the group said its major
OL,8,Foverhaul will see it reduce its number
OL,9,Fof plants from 17 to 10 by 2027.
OL,11,FNissan currently employs around 6,000
OL,12,Fpeople with its factory in Sunderland.
OL,13,FIt remains unclear as to how this news
OL,14,Fcould impact the site, with a
OL,15,Fspokesperson saying: "We are currently
OL,16,Fin detailed study within the company
OL,17,Fregarding the announced plant
OL,18,Fclosures. At this stage, we are not
OL,19,Fable to inform you which plants will
OL,20,Fbe affected."
