OL,3,CCautious optimism for Nissan in
OL,4,CSunderland despite 20,000 global job
OL,5,Closses
OL,7,FHowever, during a press conference
OL,8,Ftoday (13 May), Nissan president and
OL,9,Fchief executive Ivan Espinosa said:
OL,10,F"In Europe, we will strengthen our
OL,11,Fpresence by assembling more electric
OL,12,Fmodels in Sunderland."
OL,14,FThe firm said the shake-up will help
OL,15,F"create a leaner, more resilient
OL,16,Fbusiness" as it also cautioned over
OL,17,Fthe impact of US President Donald
OL,18,FTrump's plans for 25% tariffs on cars
OL,19,Fimported into the US.
