OL,3,CCautious optimism for Nissan in
OL,4,CSunderland despite 20,000 global job
OL,5,Closses
OL,7,FMr Espinosa said: "In the face of
OL,8,Fchallenging full-year 2024 performance
OL,9,Fand rising variable costs compounded
OL,10,Fby an uncertain environment, we must
OL,11,Fprioritise self-improvement with
OL,12,Fgreater urgency and speed, aiming for
OL,13,Fprofitability that relies less on
OL,14,Fvolume.
OL,16,F"As new management, we are taking a
OL,17,Fprudent approach to reassess our
OL,18,Ftargets and actively seek every
OL,19,Fpossible opportunity to implement and
OL,20,Fensure a robust recovery.
