OL,7,FA Government spokesperson said: "We
OL,8,Fare taking significant action to back
OL,9,FBritish carmakers and protect jobs as
OL,10,Fwe deliver on the Plan for Change `
OL,11,Ffrom announcing over #2 billion to
OL,12,Fsupport manufacturers in the switch to
OL,13,Felectric vehicles and giving them more
OL,14,Fflexibility in the ZEV mandate to do
OL,15,Fso, to securing landmark trade deals
OL,16,Fwith the US and India which will cut
OL,17,Ftariffs and create new export
OL,18,Fopportunities. Our upcoming Industrial
OL,19,FStrategy will also set out a long-term
OL,20,Fplan to support our manufacturers
OL,21,Ffurther.
